<bibRefCitation author="Kruger, M." box="[890,1046,1385,1410]" pageId="0" pageNumber="447" refId="ref2015" refString="Kruger, M. (2015) Generic classification of Afrotropical footman moths sensu stricto (Lepidoptera: Erebidae: Arctiinae: Lithosiini (partim. )). Transvaal Museum Monograph. Vol. 15. Ditsong National Museum of Natural History, Pretoria, 176 pp." type="book" year="2015">Krüger (2015)</bibRefCitation>
